    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or smudge anywhere\u2014it's been babied since day one. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
